prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D artwork for a birthday card front cover, dreamy fantasy anime style. A cartoon illustration of a young East Asian woman (Lao Lao, from reference photo) in her early 20s with long, straight dark brown hair parted on the side, wearing thin-rimmed glasses and smiling happily. She is depicted as a queen, wearing an elegant gown and a crown, sitting on an ornate golden throne. She is playfully bonking a jester on the head with a toy scepter. The jester is a cartoon illustration of a young Southeast Asian man (Jordan, from reference photo) in his early 20s with short, messy black hair, a joyful big smile, and wearing a colorful jester's hat and costume. He is kneeling beside the throne, feigning being bonked. The scene has a magical atmosphere with soft pastel colors and enchanting fairy-tale qualities. A whimsical banner floats above the throne with the text "Another Year of Ruling". In the center of the image, the words "Happy Birthday" are written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. The entire image has a lighthearted and funny tone. --ar 5:7 --style raw --seed 1234 --v 6.0

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
